Discount.Description: You will have 40 days from the day you buy your policy to establish your Kemper Direct by bringing another policyholder to Kemper Direct. Don’t worry. It’s easy, and we’ll help you.
Discount.Name: Network<sup>®</sup>

Discount.Description: The more you pay up-front, the more you save. Get this discount on your auto insurance policy when you pay more of your premium up front. The larger your down payment, the greater your discount.
Discount.Name: Preferred Payer

Discount.Description: Save on your auto insurance policy (and save some trees!). Get this discount when you provide a valid email address, sign your policy documents online and enroll in our EasyPay automatic payment service.
Discount.Name: Free-A-Tree<sup>®</sup>

Discount.Description: Save money just for switching to Kemper Direct. With this discount, we reward your loyalty to your previous carrier based on how long you were with them. Retro never looked so good.
Discount.Name: Retro Loyalty

Discount.Description: We like rewarding good driving. You get this discount if you have been continuously insured for 12 months or more, and you haven’t had any chargeable accidents or violations during the past three years.
Discount.Name: Safe & Sound<sup>®</sup>

Discount.Description: We think happy couples make good drivers and deserve a discount. And for any couples who are less than happy, perk up - you get this discount, too. Marriages, as well as legally recognized civil unions and domestic partnerships qualify.
Discount.Name: Happily Married

Discount.Description: Get this discount if you belong to any of the groups affiliated with the [Kemper Direct/Teachers/Partnership Direct] family of companies
Discount.Name: Group

Discount.Description: Get this discount when you insure more than one vehicle on the same policy. This is just one of the many ways we reward our loyal customers.
Discount.Name: Multi-Car

Discount.Description: Get this discount if your vehicle is equipped with a device that will help prevent theft losses.
Discount.Name: Anti-Theft

Discount.Description: Get this discount if you are age 55 or older, have recently completed a state-approved accident prevention course, and do not have any chargeable accidents or violations.
Discount.Name: Mature Driver

Discount.Description: Welcome back is for previous policyholders.
Discount.Name: Welcome Back

Discount.Description: Come Back and Save is for return quoters.
Discount.Name: Come Back and Save
